#!N  #!Rdxgic DXGetInvalidCount #!N #!N Function #!N #!N Returns 
the number of invalid elements in an invalid-component handle. #!N #!N 
Syntax #!N  #!F-adobe-times-bold-r-normal--18*   #include <dx/dx.h> int DXGetInvalidCount(InvalidComponentHandle handle) #!EF #!N #!N 
Functional Details #!N #!N Elements that are multiply invalidated are counted 
once. #!N #!N Return Value #!N #!N Returns the number of 
